About this issue: The llms.txt file helps AI search engines better understand your website's content by providing LLM-friendly information. This file offers a short summary, guidance, and links to other useful resources. How to fix: 1. Create an llms.txt file. 2. Place it in your website's root directory and ensure the file is accessible. 3. Refer to llmstxt.org for examples and tips on how to properly create and manage it.